name: Incoin
description: $in is an art-driven meme project launched on Jup Studio, built around original, hand-made, non-AI artwork. The artist behind $in is new to crypto but brings a unique style and vision that stands out in a space often dominated by AI-generated content. The project’s purpose is to create a community that values intentional art, slower appreciation, and cultural identity over hype cycles. $in represents humility, curiosity, and relatability through its character “in,” which embodies the idea of being small, unassuming, yet easy to root for. The utility of $in lies in its cultural value. Original artwork tied to a community that supports real creators, and in positioning itself as a project where members can slow down and enjoy something beautiful in the midst of a chaotic market.
